jun kyxol qe jlu, nimxix tipumal tuʼn t-xi tqʼamaʼn kye soldad te Imperial tuʼn kymeltzʼaj, nimxix in tzaj xobʼ xjal tuʼn
tun t-xi kyq´o´n ky-xob´il kyxolx. Aqeju xjal in che aqʼunan toj bark aju otoq che kubʼ t-ximen jun maj, e kyaj ten
n-chi q´ojin, n-chi b´aj t-xiten extzen n-chi oq toj xob´ajil tej t-xi tka´yin aju q´eq t-xb´alun —armadura aju, maske q´eq t-xilen,
mya ch´ixme ikyx t-xmakal ik tza´n qe ximb´etz n-chi b´et toj qwi´.
