ti´j jlu?
Jun plaj te, jun tnej n-chi ch´iy, n-chi ch´iy mas ex mas mya b´a´n tu´n t-xi´
mya b´antni. Nya jun nya bʼaʼn in kubʼ kynaʼn kuʼxun ik tzeʼn te, noqtzun tuʼnj, tuʼn junjun tiquʼn mintiʼ kubʼ kynaʼn Lucas
tz´elx tniky´a ti´j qa nimxix tipumal toj twitz twitz alkyexku juntl tamiw.
