b´inchama junjen t-landspeeder. Aye xjal te t-xaq a´ n-chi tzaj ky-xob´il, noqtzun ayetzi´n n-chi meltz´aj toj
nimxix kyajlal. jun landspeeder mya jun oyaj n-chi tzaj q´o´n, extzen t-xelju, aye jawas mya.
N-chi kub´ tq´o´n kykab´il tq´ob´ tib´aj ttzi´ toj jun tten mya b´a´n, a Kenobi n-chi tzaj t-xew extzen n-chi etz t-xo´n jun
jun tq´ajq´ajel mya twitz tx´otx´ aju b´ant tu´n Luke tu´n t-xi t-xo´n tib´. “A jlu il ti´j tu´n t-xi t-xq´uqin junjun laggards tu´n t-xi´ b´et toj jun amb´il,” aju
